{"word":"G1362 - διπλοῦς - diploûs - dip-looce' - Double","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διπλοῦς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diploûs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dip-looce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Double</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இரட்டிப்பான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"twofold, double"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1364 - δίς - dís - dece/1364\">G1364</a> and (probably) the base of <a href=\"#/G4119 - πλείων - pleíōn - pli-own/4119\">G4119</a>; <i>two fold:</i> - double, two-fold more.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}